rows.label: qst200403_msg0001
rows.name:
A loan shark?
Huh... No clue.

rows.label: qst200403_msg0002
rows.name:
But there's definitely dudes here that
you shouldn't tangle with.

rows.label: qst200403_msg0003
rows.name:
They've been going around town lately,
pretend-hurting themselves to extort
money from hardworking people.

rows.label: qst200403_msg0004
rows.name:
What's worse though is that there's a
doctor working with them, "charging"
the "injured" stupidly high fees.

rows.label: qst200403_msg0005
rows.name:
You'd do well to steer well clear of
that kind of noise, fellas!
